.SH BUGS
The automated pipeline may time out on maximal-scope ob3ects with slow providers.
Increase
.B --retries
and use a faster model.
.PP
The Frobenius gate at phase 2 is strict:
.I \[*m]\(co\[*d] = id
must hold on the
.I entire
source, not a subset.
Systems with deliberate irreversibility (IFIX operations, side-effectful I/O)
must isolate the irreversible component and verify the roundtrip on the
reversible core separately.
